Description: GUIs for making (S)VCDs and DVDs
 Tovid can help you create your own DVDs, VCDs, and SVCDs for
 playback on your home DVD player.
 .
 tovid converts arbitrary video formats into (S)VCD/DVD-compliant MPEG
 files, and can help with menu creation and disc authoring.
 .
 This package contains these graphical user interfaces for tovid:
   * tovidgui -- a wx-GTK+ (GNOME-like) front-end for tovid
   * todiscgui -- a Tkinter front-end for todisc
 .
 Homepage: http://tovid.wikia.com
